Hayley Grimes found Baby Peter in a Norfolk pond in 1988 and was accused of being his mother . 
  She was just a teenager when she found the body wrapped in a blanket and Sainsbury's bag . 
  The boy's mother was arrested after police used DNA profiling to trace her . 
  She told officers she had put the body in the lake after a stillbirth . 
  Baby Peter has been reburied at Weasenham St Peter church . 
 